    <p><anchor n="X.88.1646.0225b04"/><lb ed="X" n="0225b04"/><persName key="A017656">范儼</persName><placeName key="PL000000011514">仁和</placeName>人。居常蔬食。不牽世緣。曰百年旅泊耳。尚<lb ed="X" n="0225b05"/>何求哉。日誦法華經。手書一部。求生<placeName key="PL000000055477">淨土</placeName>。<date from-iso="1107-02-02" key="j21254152126890" to-iso="1111-02-16">大觀中</date>忽<lb ed="X" n="0225b06"/>見<persName key="A003079">普賢</persName>乘六牙白象放金色光謂<persName key="A017656">儼</persName>曰。汝常誦法華。<lb ed="X" n="0225b07"/>念<persName key="A002843">彌陀佛</persName>。得生<placeName key="PL000000055477">淨土</placeName>。故來相報。越一夕。覩眾聖授手。<lb ed="X" n="0225b08"/>就座合掌而逝(佛祖統記)。</p> 
    
